Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:16.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,總帥要用筆了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:17.32,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,勝者是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.53,0:00:18.74,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,哪邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.58,0:00:27.58,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,勝者是黑木場涼選手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:32.55,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,田所的料理並沒有讓總帥…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.97,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒讓他「爆衣」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.35,0:00:36.61,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,到場的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.97,0:00:39.64,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的比賽已經全部完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.22,0:00:43.23,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第三第四場比賽將會在明天舉行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:45.98,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,回去的路上請注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.85,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,去接田所吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:48.94,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:50.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 悠姬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.36,0:00:52.82,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.49,0:00:57.49,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,黑木場君 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:03.41,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂 惠就像被野狗襲擊的兔子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.10,0:01:08.38,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了 田所惠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.03,0:01:09.67,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,北條同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.16,0:01:11.12,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:13.21,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和黑木場那樣子交鋒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.62,0:01:14.90,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很勇敢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.15,0:01:17.47,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看來並不是僥倖通過預賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.86,0:01:25.64,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有勞各位的審查了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:27.85,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接送的專車已經到位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:28.94,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊請
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:33.44,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,爺爺 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.98,0:01:36.70,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事 想去趟廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.21,0:01:42.28,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,她叫 田所惠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.87,0:01:45.54,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,看來那孩子身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.96,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,還有著深不可測的潛能嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:52.88,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不覺中就「爆衣」了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.52,0:01:55.60,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第92期
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.05,0:01:57.59,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,「玉」的時代
